Bradesco Confident It Will Buy Carrefour Bank Stake, FT Reports

-- B y   A l a n   P u r k i s s
-- 
2011-03-21T05:28:25Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-21/bradesco-confident-it-will-buy-carrefour-bank-stake-ft-reports.html
  Banco Bradesco SA (BBDC4)  is confident it
will succeed in buying a stake in  Carrefour SA (CA) ’s financial unit
in Brazil, the Financial Times reported, citing Luiz Carlos Trabuco, the Brazilian bank’s chief executive officer.  Brazil’s  Itau-Unibanco Holding SA (ITUB4)  and Spain’s  Banco
Santander SA (SAN)  are also interested in the unit, the newspaper
cited Trabuco as saying.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Alan Purkiss in London on   apurkiss@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at 
 ckeatinge@bloomberg.net . 